<recipe>
<title>
Pumpkin Pie Smoothie
</title>
<details>

</details>
<ingredients>
2 c. Silk Almond and Coconut Milk Original or Unsweetened
2 5.3 oz. Silk Vanilla Dairy-Free Yogurt Alternative
1/2 c. Sprouts pumpkin puree
1 tsp. pumpkin pie spice
2-3 T. maple syrup optional
Kashi Honey Flax Granola
</ingredients>
<instructions>
In a large blender, combine milk, yogurt alternative, pumpkin puree, spice, and maple syrup, if using. 
Blend until smooth. 
Pour into four glasses. 
Top with Kashi, and serve. 
</instructions>
</recipe>
